Screenwriter: Prabhu Deva, Prabhu Deva, Sunil Agrawal, Ravi Sundaram, Shiraz Ahmed, Prabhudheva, Sunil Agarwal, Ravi S Sundaram
Production Co: Eros International, Eros Worldwide, Next Gen Films
Synopsis: Rajkumar, an aimless youth, works for a drug baron and is sent to kill a rival dealer. His life is changed forever when he meets Chanda, and has no idea she is the adopted daughter of the man he is supposed to kill.
Title: Rambo Rajkumar
